\v 51 \w Hadad|strong="H1908"\w* \w died|strong="H4191"\w*.
\s1 Tribal Chiefs \w of|strong="H4191"\w* Edom
\p \w The|strong="H1961"\w* tribal chiefs \w of|strong="H4191"\w* Edom \w were|strong="H1961"\w*:
\p \w Timna|strong="H8555"\w*, \w Alvah|strong="H5933"\w*, \w Jetheth|strong="H3509"\w*,
