\v 54 \w Magdiel|strong="H4025"\w*, \w Iram|strong="H5902"\w*. These were the tribal chiefs of Edom.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 These \w were|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H1121"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w*:
